title: Harvard's Education - Suzanne Brockmann.epub
description: FInCOM agent P. J. Richards is being given the opportunity to view the no-women-allowed world of the navy SEALs from the inside, and she can't afford any distractions--especially not Senior Chief "Harvard" Becker. A toughened SEAL, Harvard believes there's no room for women in a combat zone, but P.J. is determined to teach him a thing or two.... She just doesn't expect the same in return.
